column16: Adam Frazier flies out to left fielder Chase d'Arnaud.
Starling Marte singles on a line drive to left fielder Chase d'Arnaud.   Francisco Cervelli scores.    John Jaso to 2nd.
John Jaso grounds into a force out, shortstop Dansby Swanson to second baseman Brandon Phillips.   Francisco Cervelli to 3rd.    Josh Harrison out at 2nd.    John Jaso to 1st.
Jordy Mercer flies out to center fielder Ender Inciarte.
Josh Harrison reaches on a fielding error by second baseman Brandon Phillips.   Francisco Cervelli to 2nd.

Yoenis Cespedes grounds into a force out, first baseman Freddie Freeman to shortstop Dansby Swanson.   Jose Reyes scores.    Asdrubal Cabrera out at 2nd.  Yoenis Cespedes advances to 1st, on a throwing error by shortstop Dansby Swanson.
Asdrubal Cabrera singles on a ground ball to left fielder Matt Kemp.   Michael Conforto scores.    Jose Reyes to 2nd.
Jose Reyes singles on a ground ball to center fielder Ender Inciarte.   Michael Conforto to 2nd.
Travis d'Arnaud grounds out, third baseman Adonis Garcia to first baseman Freddie Freeman.
Yoenis Cespedes walks.   Jose Reyes to 3rd.    Asdrubal Cabrera to 2nd.
